<section class="component  ">

  
      <div class="component-multi-column-text">

        
    <div class="component-description">
                    <h2 id="biological-safety" class="__title invisible">Biological Safety</h2>
                    </div>

        <div class="component-multi-column-text__columns">
            
                <div class="component-multi-column-text__column component-multi-column-text__column--three">

                                            <h3 id="policies-and-regulations" class="component-multi-column-text__column__title visible">
                          Policies and Regulations
                        </h3>
                    
                    
                    <div class="component-multi-column-text__content">
                        <p><a href="https://uofi.box.com/s/8ew1nnl8yqrw7r58pt81kaqm1od27ak4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UIC BioSafety Manual</a></p>
<p><a href="https://uofi.box.com/s/hoe7e8of3pjdiv16jpshdajq0szwjf9x" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UIC Bloodborne Pathogen Exposure Control Plan</a></p>
<p><a href="https://uofi.box.com/s/8orotsikk1st9s5g7sgq1nabci4dsh7w" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UIC Pandemic Flu Planning</a></p>
<p><a href="https://uofi.box.com/s/mpi3bb6mt3fu76e1r8glcqf6e871x3n0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Biosafety Cabinet Policy</a></p>
<p><a href="https://uofi.box.com/s/luhaqjc75sfl0fws1ed81p1ehb874db1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UIC Approved NSF Certified Biosafety Cabinet Certifiers</a></p>
<p><a href="http://research.uic.edu/compliance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OVCR, ACC, IBC, Controlled Substances in Animals and IRB</a></p>
<p><a href="https://uofi.box.com/s/vd4zdnqjxysk1rua13dxpsc22na6iklm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Medical Waste Information Sheet</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

                    </div>

                                    </div>

            
                <div class="component-multi-column-text__column component-multi-column-text__column--three">

                                            <h3 id="training" class="component-multi-column-text__column__title visible">
                          Training
                        </h3>
                    
                    
                    <div class="component-multi-column-text__content">
                        <p><a href="http://ehso.uic.edu/training/annual-bloodborne-pathogen-refresher-training/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bloodborne Pathogen and Needlestick Prevention – Online</a></p>
<p><a href="http://ehso.uic.edu/training/initial-bloodborne-pathogen-training/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Initial Bloodborne Pathogen and Needlestick Prevention – In class</a></p>
<p>Project/Lab Specific Biosafety &#8211; Contact biosafety@uic.edu</p>
<p><a href="http://ehso.uic.edu/training/biological-safety-cabinets-training/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Biological Safety Cabinet Training</a></p>
<p><a href="http://ehso.uic.edu/training/shipping-hazardous-materials-training/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Infectious &amp; Biological Material Shipping</a></p>
<p><a href="http://ehso.uic.edu/training/bloodborne-pathogen-training-schedule/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bloodborne Pathogen Initial Training</a></p>
<p>PPE Training &#8211; Contact biosafety@uic.edu</p>

                    </div>

                                    </div>

            
                <div class="component-multi-column-text__column component-multi-column-text__column--three">

                                            <h3 id="tools-resources" class="component-multi-column-text__column__title visible">
                          Tools/Resources
                        </h3>
                    
                    
                    <div class="component-multi-column-text__content">
                        <p><a href="https://absa.org/riskgroups/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Risk Group Database &#8211; ABSA</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.osha.gov/SLTC/bloodbornepathogens/standards.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bloodborne Pathogen and Needlestick Standard– OSHA</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/biosafety/publications/bmbl5/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Biosafety in Microbiological and Biomedical Laboratory &#8211; CDC</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.selectagents.gov/Regulations.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Federal Select Agent Program</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/public-health/services/laboratory-biosafety-biosecurity/pathogen-safety-data-sheets-risk-assessment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pathogen Safety Data Sheets and Risk Assessment &#8211; PHAC</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/phpr/ipp/index.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CDC Import Permits for Pathogens and Infectious Agents</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.aphis.usda.gov/aphis/ourfocus/animalhealth/sa_program_overview?1dmy&amp;urile=wcm%3apath%3a%2Faphis_content_library%2Fsa_our_focus%2Fsa_animal_health%2Fsa_import_into_us%2Fct_organisms_and%2B_vectors">USDA/APHIS Import Permits</a></p>
<p><a href="http://brl.uic.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Biological Resources Laboratory</a></p>
<p><a href="https://absa.org/">American Biological Safety Association International</a></p>
<p><a href="https://absa.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">American Biological Safety Association International Resources</a></p>

                    </div>

                                    </div>

                    </div>
    </div>

  
</section>

    

</div>

